and canceled the agreement.

9
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:18,920
Kwanrin.

10
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:21,160
Khem is staying with you, isn't she?

11
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,440
She's not with me.

12
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,120
Please, Dad.

13
00:00:28,590 --> 00:00:30,240
I need her.

14
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,500
I love her.

15
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:34,800
Do you hear that I love her?

16
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:38,640
Can you please help me find Khem?

17
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:46,680
I love Khem. Do you hear me?

18
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,760
Can you please come back to me?

19
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:15,160
Stop speaking falsely about Prapai

20
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:18,320
and get out of here.

21
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:21,320
I no longer want to see your face.

22
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:27,000
Take care, Rin.

23
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,680
Let's have dinner with me.

24
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,000
I don't want to.

25
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,440
I'm not hungry.

26
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,280
You've lost a lot of weight, Rin.

27
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,360
Let's go and have something.

28
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:52,200
Then I'll tell you where she is.

29
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,400
You've found her?

30
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,800
Take a shower.

31
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,760
Dress up

32
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,080
and come have a meal with me.

33
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,920
After that, let's bring her home.

34
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,840
Promise?

35
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,920
Thank you, Dad.

36
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,120
Are you full?

37
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,360
That's nice.

38
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:56,560
Now, I'll fulfill the promise.

39
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,840
Please have a seat.

40
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,600
Kwanrin's paying us a visit.

41
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,880
She's going to tell me where Khem is.

42
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:17,440
Mr. Wasin actually has been asking me
several times already

43
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,440
to get me to tell him where Khem is.

44
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,720
Yet, every time, I lied

45
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,560
and said I had no idea.

46
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,640
I'm sorry for keeping you
waiting until now.

47
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,600
You actually did that, Dad?

48
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,640
Rin,

49
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,360
I'm really scared, dear.

50
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,760
I almost lost you once,

51
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,880
and I'm not gonna let it happen again.

52
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:54,060
If something were to happen to you,

53
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,960
I wouldn't be able to go on.

54
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:05,200
I'm sorry, Dad.

55
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:11,040
I promise that no matter what happens
from now on,

56
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:14,000
I won't do it again.

57
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,840
That's all I ask.

58
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:30,080
Kwanrin.

59
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:33,160
Can you please tell me

60
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,520
where Khem is?

61
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:41,800
Khem actually told me
not to tell you where she is.

62
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:45,240
I've also promised that I wouldn't,

63
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:59,400
but I don't want her
to suffer forever either.

64
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,400
So...

65
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:07,000
I'll tell you where Khem is.

66
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,080
These are all the details
I have about where she is.

67
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,120
The reason I'm telling you
everything today is that

68
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,080
if I were to tell you later,

69
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,280
you might not get to see her again.

70
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,520
What do you mean?

71
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,920
She's moving overseas.

72
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:38,240
If you choose to go after her today,

73
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,200
you'll still be able to find her.

74
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:45,480
Thank you very much, Kwanrin.

75
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,640
I promise I'll do my best

76
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,560
to bring her back home.

77
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,320
Thank you, Dad.

78
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,320
Thank you.

